{"tid":700570,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普指北韓不再是美國最大及最危險問題","createTime":"2018-06-13T12:21:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-13T13:35:36.000Z","uid":5195,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"2aa109dc75082dae1d750b0f42e3e81491fbb104","tid":700570,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T12:21:41.000Z","msg":"特朗普指北韓不再是美國最大及最危險問題<br />\n13.06.2018 18:46<br />\n美國總統特朗普與北韓領導人金正恩，昨日在新加坡簽署聯合聲明，特朗普承諾向北韓提供安全保障，金正恩重申會落實半島無核化；特朗普乘坐空軍一號專機返國，他多度在社交網誌帖文，感謝金正恩在無核化踏出果敢一步，指北韓再不會構成核威脅，所有人會感覺目前比他就職時更安全，他指，就職前有人認定美國將會與北韓開戰，總統奧巴馬就指，北韓是美國最大及最危險的問題，目前不再是這樣，特朗普又形容與金正恩的會晤，是有趣及非常正面的經歷，話北韓未來具有巨大潛能。"},{"pid":"e3e4f205600cefbdb8f9bebc4f06d8f2e0c3e61d","tid":700570,"uid":134323,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T12:22:50.000Z","msg":"大國掘起 中國成為美國最大及最危險問題"},{"pid":"800eeb84e34becae3818ff0fb7ee4ce348104f43","tid":700570,"uid":24140,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T12:23:29.000Z","msg":"鄰國 GG <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa7c578b3041b93f99b473339935b7300468b581","tid":700570,"uid":46933,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T12:24:11.000Z","msg":"聚焦中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c41f6d3bb749f2adf0517de7823e7dba6cbc2ff8","tid":700570,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T12:25:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d6395aaa41a7dab8756acbaf2e7ee0d2058eefcc","tid":700570,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T12:39:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3b8d87215a81d7804112b38c64f536749c34161a","tid":700570,"uid":29314,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T12:40:00.000Z","msg":"中國成為最大贏家"},{"pid":"0df13d6dc3d144e6bf3e4efe5644ec40eb21b25a","tid":700570,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e3e4f205600cefbdb8f9bebc4f06d8f2e0c3e61d","tid":700570